<div class="titrePage">
  <h2>{'Read me'|translate} - Contribute to Demo</h2>
</div>

<fieldset>
  <legend>{'What is it?'|translate}</legend>

<p>
{'Photos in the Piwigo demo are coming from Piwigo users all over the world.'|translate}
{'The idea is to have high quality and fresh content in the demo and give credits to Piwigo community for this contribution.'|translate}
</p>

<p>
{'In the demo, on the page of the photo, you will see a "contributed by" info with a link to the contributor website.'|translate}
{'This link will provide visibility to your Piwigo from humans and search engines as well.'|translate}
</p>

  <p><img src="plugins/contribute_to_demo/images/contributed-by.jpg"></p>

<p>
{'Once duplicated in the demo, you give permission to the Piwigo demo for displaying your photo.'|translate}
{'As a contributor, you keep the ownership of your photos.'|translate}
{'At any time, you can remove your photo with a single and immediate action.'|translate}
</p>

<p>
{'We hope you\'ll love the idea and decide to become a contributor yourself.'|translate}
{'The Piwigo project needs you to create the most appealing demo.'|translate}
{'A nice demo will attract more users.'|translate}
{'More users means more improvements to make Piwigo even more awesome!'|translate}
</p>

</fieldset>

<fieldset>
  <legend>{'How to contribute?'|translate}</legend>

<p>
{'Find a nice photo in your Piwigo and edit it.'|translate}
{'You can edit any photo either from the gallery or from the batch manager.'|translate}
{'On the edition page, click on the "contribute to demo" link.'|translate}
{'Your photo will be submitted to the Piwigo demo, pending for validation (or reject).'|translate}
</p>

  <p><img src="plugins/contribute_to_demo/images/contribute-link.png"></p>

<p>
{'The administrators of the demo manage a list of pending photos.'|translate}
{'You\'ll be notified by mail when your photo is validated.'|translate}
</p>

  <p>{'Quite easy! Let\'s start!'|translate}</p>

</fieldset>